ED_Title: Comprehensive implementation  of and follow-up to the Vienna Declaration and Programme of Action
ED_DecisionText: At its 50th plenary meeting, on 19 December 2023, the General Assembly took note of the report of the Third Committee.  (Footnote: A/78/481/Add.4.)
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the main part of the session will be contained in document A/78/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
